    <div class="svc-hero-content">
      <h1>Public Sector Partnership: Transforming Governance Through Technology</h1>
      <p>Live, production systems serving government institutions and citizens across India, delivered under the scrutiny, security requirements and compliance standards India&rsquo;s public sector demands.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

